## Cleaning in Kashmir — local context

Kashmir's seasons shape when and how Srinagar residents think about home cleanliness. Winter heating and closed windows can leave dust and soot buildup; spring and autumn are popular times for seasonal deep cleans; monsoon moisture makes bathroom and kitchen sanitization especially important. After masonry, painting, or carpentry work, fine dust settles in corners that everyday sweeping misses.

When you book through Panun Kaergar, you are hiring professionals who understand residential and small commercial cleaning in local homes. Partners arrive with appropriate supplies and methods for the job you select. You can note special requests — delicate surfaces, pet areas, nursery rooms, or office equipment zones — when you book.

