## Tips before your cleaning visit in Srinagar

A little preparation helps your booking go smoothly and gets better results on site:

- **Declutter surfaces** — clearing counters, tables, and floors lets cleaners focus on deep work.
- **Note room count and approximate size** when booking so the right team and time are allocated.
- **List priority areas** — kitchen grease, bathrooms, windows, or post-renovation dust — in your booking notes.
- **Secure valuables and documents** in a safe place before the team arrives.
- **Be home or have someone available** for the first visit to show access, water points, and any fragile items.

If you need add-on services — inside oven cleaning, balcony wash, or office desk zones — mention them when you book. For large homes or commercial spaces, a walkthrough quote on the first visit helps plan recurring schedules and budget.

